<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1036101-the-book-is-written-meticulously-by">The Book is written meticulously by Sanchit Gupta in a much enthralling way. The book won&#39;t let one to cut loose, as the story entangles in between three besties Safeena, Bilal and Deewan, three young besties with their tender hearts relishing their Kashmiriyat. 
Grab a copy of the book, as it uncovers a few unearthed facts around &#39;Kashmiriat&#39;; How can be a porter planted as a terrorist?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
